skins.selfIntroduction: I'm the big sister of the Cleveland-class... but I guess that's obvious from my name alone. I may be a light cruiser, but I can match a heavy cruiser no problem! I am gonna dominate the seas, after all!
skins.acquisition: Hello, my name is Cleveland! My dream is to one day join the Solomon Knights! I'm working hard towards that goal every day!
skins.login: Morning, Commander! How about a chocolate bar?
skins.details: I eat so much every day, but I'm not growing at all... Why...?
skins.secretaryIdle1: I've got lots of little sisters, and I love each and every one of 'em! Lemme introduce you someday!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Hey, Commander, is there a blue-haired girl in the fleet, about yea big, always staring at herself in the mirror? You mind if I go play with her?
skins.secretaryIdle3: Being this small is kind of inconvenient sometimes. ... Like when? Like when I'm trying to help somebody with something...?
skins.secretaryTouch: It's important to keep your energy up, Commander! Here, have a chocolate bar!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Huh? You wanna rub my belly?
